        <item>
            <title>1.8.1</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 12:02:20 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>29</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes

- Fixed `canopy-overrides.css` not being included in the app bundle, which caused missing CSS overrides in production builds

### Changes

- Inline bundle CSS/JS resources directly into HTML template instead of copying files to Application Support directory
- Improved error logging: missing Prism.js resources now produce warning logs instead of failing silently
- `readBundleResource` now distinguishes between "resource not found" and "resource read failed" with proper error logging
- Fixed inaccurate comment about read access scope
]]></description>
